{"tid":1314930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無用功] 上水龍豐藥房鐵閘遭噴字句　水貨店重開　篋陣再現","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:55:10.000Z","uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22eb9e8aa3dc537e905dc911384f7137c4b6fdcc","tid":1314930,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"昨日（13日）大批市民響應出席光復上水遊行，不少水貨店索性「落閘休息」避風頭，遊行結束後爆發嚴重衝突，亦有部分示威者前往水貨街的藥房閘門噴漆及叫囂，場面混亂。今晨7時許，警方接獲報案，指上水新發街的找換店及龍琛路的藥房，其閉路電視被淋黑油及噴黑，記者今早重返上址查看，發現光復過後，各水貨店已陸續開店，受影響的藥房亦繼續營業，「篋陣」畫面重現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031335/org/05dfde745a5e4190af7fd3ee8b9feb22.jpg/CPifQ-KOXFcFWlOIruIm3XFIkoeyXlge1gOAvNYDgLw?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031335%2Forg%2F05dfde745a5e4190af7fd3ee8b9feb22.jpg%2FCPifQ-KOXFcFWlOIruIm3XFIkoeyXlge1gOAvNYDgLw%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=2d4d0cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>示威者噴上「中國人飲中國奶粉」字句</strong><br />\n<br />\n受昨日光復遊行影響，上水大批水貨店提早關門，有示威者在遊行後到目標店舖噴漆。今早9時許，記者重返現場查看，發現各水貨店及受影響的藥房等店舖已陸續開店，門口亦陸續出現熟悉的「篋陣」畫面。部分店舖職員開店時，發現門口被噴油漆。位於新豐路的龍豐藥房，其鐵閘遭人噴上「中國人飲中國奶粉」的字句，有四個鎖被灌膠水，職員報案尋求警方協助；此外，同樣位於新豐路的新龍豐藥房，昨日被示威者拆去招牌，門口亦被人噴上「反送中」字眼，職員同樣於今早報警求助，惟拒絕受訪。而位於龍琛路的藥房，有職員表示鎖頭被人貼上招紙，閉路電視亦遭人噴黑。位於新發街的找換店，其閉路電視亦被人淋黑油，職員報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031336/org/2da22a66ef1dbac2979cc769b2a6f7bb.jpg/-0ZzC52LQtVKQX9ZIXQGu7phm-OXa7KEpQMvDKUDLww?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031336%2Forg%2F2da22a66ef1dbac2979cc769b2a6f7bb.jpg%2F-0ZzC52LQtVKQX9ZIXQGu7phm-OXa7KEpQMvDKUDLww%3Fv%3Dw800&h=b2ff946f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031344/org/46d5da99867c80f2fed50a944ae549f6.jpg/66TkunAtD_26L57D5eILVgZ4q2Gt9xXFlJONp5STjac\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031344%2Forg%2F46d5da99867c80f2fed50a944ae549f6.jpg%2F66TkunAtD_26L57D5eILVgZ4q2Gt9xXFlJONp5STjac&h=c733a1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031342/org/2d7cec0ebe6360845d3e423434913f22.jpg/PYYv1J4IMtROM-zQMuAJVclJxmiHIwo8yI-j-8iPo_s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031342%2Forg%2F2d7cec0ebe6360845d3e423434913f22.jpg%2FPYYv1J4IMtROM-zQMuAJVclJxmiHIwo8yI-j-8iPo_s&h=f401ac21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031340/org/5d8d25c1741367e232bbd6ce9b3c1c14.jpg/-vALTYPrP4KernyT5B5A4Qnd-CU6N9mDUSBjIFEgYyA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031340%2Forg%2F5d8d25c1741367e232bbd6ce9b3c1c14.jpg%2F-vALTYPrP4KernyT5B5A4Qnd-CU6N9mDUSBjIFEgYyA&h=faccb68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水打工仔斥政府漠視民情<br />\n<br />\n至於位於龍豐藥房附近的報紙檔今日照常營業，檔主衛先生稱支持反水貨客行動，並指昨日遊行大致和平，自己亦有朋友及街坊參與示威，惟他形容遊行後的示威者較「有組織」，戴有頭盔及眼罩，手持旗幟在上址揮動，亦曾與警員爭執。他的報紙檔在上址擺檔約60年，他坦言水貨客的出現對附近舖位如茶餐廳的租金升幅有直接影響，對他的生意則影響不大。在上址上班、任職物流業的龍先生指自己昨日不在區內，他直言支持整頓上水風氣，「十幾年前呢度啲嘢冇咁貴，交通亦冇咁擠塞」，形容是政府漠視民情的惡果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031343/org/d84028eb5b5d8158b0d46de2a2cc1b84.jpg/beJygBCTDQy0n2yEay0D09GrzOu7FgGG4afmGuGn5ho\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031343%2Forg%2Fd84028eb5b5d8158b0d46de2a2cc1b84.jpg%2FbeJygBCTDQy0n2yEay0D09GrzOu7FgGG4afmGuGn5ho&h=1fbd4696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031341/org/7851541ed6867151cac7e4bc456c4e8e.jpg/avs7CssFJUcXyv4XVg_v_yeWVVF9DhQLCcz7AQnM-wE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031341%2Forg%2F7851541ed6867151cac7e4bc456c4e8e.jpg%2Favs7CssFJUcXyv4XVg_v_yeWVVF9DhQLCcz7AQnM-wE&h=ba6cf4e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031345/org/f9a1db3002c3e92804f15060db31f7f0.jpg/QC5FRPthyrGUOjYQlfS3Mi31UEaUrFV7qRIQN6kSEDc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031345%2Forg%2Ff9a1db3002c3e92804f15060db31f7f0.jpg%2FQC5FRPthyrGUOjYQlfS3Mi31UEaUrFV7qRIQN6kSEDc&h=7bb2bfdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3031338/org/91738259d66322e4ef7c3bf0b3dfb921.jpg/VYuCEaHq9k1kt5dcxGFB_XAgkZg5BhyJ1VF4GdVReBk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3031338%2Forg%2F91738259d66322e4ef7c3bf0b3dfb921.jpg%2FVYuCEaHq9k1kt5dcxGFB_XAgkZg5BhyJ1VF4GdVReBk&h=cd81da9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>藥房職員：唔好針對我哋啲小市民</strong><br />\n<br />\n位於符興街的一間藥房，其職員管小姐表示，昨午3時許聽到外面傳來哄動聲音便下閘，至傍晚6時許，見街道上的示威者已散去，欲重新開閘，惟不足半小時，即惹來示威者前來，故最後重新下閘。管小姐表示，每逢周六普遍較多人光顧藥房，暫時未清楚損失數字，直言「閂咗閘梗係有損失，唔使舖租唔使人工咩？」該店在上址開業三十年，管小姐指即使2012年光復上水行動，沒有完全關上鐵閘，亦未有遇上如昨日的情況，擔心若有下次示威遊行會出現同樣情況，只能下閘應對，「你哋出嚟遊行，我哋唔反對，有咩心聲講出嚟，唔好對（針對）我哋啲小市民，我哋最緊要有工開有糧出」。另一名職員則表示，「幾十年都冇遇過呢個情況，成個地方閂晒門！」又直言「你唔啱咪去政府總部示威，有乜理由對我哋啲小市民咁」。"},{"pid":"bcaf88270e9bdc9a1e66a76caf981e8422c3a3e2","tid":1314930,"uid":224836,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"收兵啦針對你地小市民<br />\n講真果到開藥房同職員 所撚有都係有份造成水貨客既局面架<br />\n最撚應該打把係開藥房果堆仆街"},{"pid":"769cfd15660a1e88fa963807e8cf2dfc6b86bdd1","tid":1314930,"uid":98958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"呢個真係無計<br />\n只可以1823<br />\n阻街 <br />\n隨地掉垃圾<br />\n違泊<br />\n走私<br />\n乜撚都報<br />\n我地又唔洗出手"},{"pid":"7a69ee84179d14b50a9a872c0ca475467a665672","tid":1314930,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0960600467126efb3670551550ce4219614c8bc","tid":1314930,"uid":272072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n唯有1823 自己救！"},{"pid":"3b089a7ab459bd00b2e89a6c47056781036a06e0","tid":1314930,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"龍豐藥房老闆之前係唔係比自己伙記攞刀劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d7a23a051ff7f1cd211231a6106a96a7f26623","tid":1314930,"uid":57710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1d2412b4192879d1325c14323dbef18c2e7ca79","tid":1314930,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a69ee84179d14b50a9a872c0ca475467a665672","tid":1314930,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"人講兩句你就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc14236c8fe8c89353be3cc2c2677bb858ad5f1f","tid":1314930,"uid":119413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}